Vision statement: It is all too common that the best jump scares are reserved for Halloween.
Which is fair, however, what about the rest of the year? Just like you, we here at Software Core Principles games are 
adrenaline junkies who love a good jump scare anytime of the year. That’s why we created our Jack-in-the-box rush room. 
A room with a simple task, find the jump scare. Seems simple right? Well where’s the fun in simple?! In this room you will 
interact with different objects until you find the jump scare, building that adrenaline for the right moment. 
Through each level, the number of objects will increase and the scares get bigger. To semi-quote R.L Stein: 
“Player beware, you’re in for a scare.”

Display a warning message: This game is intended for adrenaline junkies who enjoy jumpscares. 
This game is appropriate for participants ages 10-99. Warning if you have any health conditions 
that can be exacerbated by being scared please do not play this game. 
